        <li>Hands‑on exposure across 15+ states with multiple government departments</li>
        <li>End‑to‑end expertise in DPR and RFP drafting, procurement models, and contract management</li>
        <li>Strong capabilities in project and program management lifecycle including PMU support</li>
        <li>Domain experience across Telecom, IT, Skill Development, ERP, and software implementations</li>
        <li>10‑member consulting team with 10+ years of Big Four consulting experience</li>
        <li>Governance‑first, compliance‑driven, and audit‑ready execution approach</li>
